            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chicken is lightly browned, add the <strong>curry paste</strong> to the pan with your <strong>ground turmeric</strong> and cook for 2-3 min or until fragrant</p><p>Meanwhile, dissolve your <strong>chicken stock mix</strong> in 150ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[225ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[300ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p>",
