    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Stir the <strong>chopped mango</strong> through the <strong>chicken curry</strong> and serve over the <strong>basmati rice</strong></p><p>Tip: For fancy presentation, press the rice into a small bowl and turn out</p><p>Garnish with your <strong>nigella seeds</strong>,<strong> chopped chilli</strong> (not a fan of spice? Just add a little!) and <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>lime wedges</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
